🎶 Contains Music

There is this beautiful tree right outside my mama’s house which blossoms every Spring which i can look at for hours 🌸 
This Spring I thought why not capture it before something happens to it. Why did i think of this you may ask? 
Because we don’t know what’s going to happen tomorrow yet we still are making plans for years and years ahead in the future, why can’t we just focus on the Beautiful things that we already have in front of us and appreciate them while we can 🤍
Same is for the people in our lives, Appreciate them, love them and tell them how you feel about them, while you can.

Can’t wait to bother you for the rest of our lives, goodluck! 😎✌🏻
Don’t forget to say MashaaAllah 🤗

Here’s to growing old together with our Orhaan, InshaaAllah 🤗
